Pandas () () (DataFrame)

DataFrame

x

  • (2d list)
  • numpy (ndarray)
  • (dict)numpy
  • (DataFrame)

DataFrame()

  • x
  • index
    • idx = range(0, x.shape[0])
    • (integer) (string) (datetime)
  • columns
    • col = range(0, x.shape[1])

2 iloc i:j, k:l i+1 j k+1 l
